author: Fextralife
description:
First Berserker Khazan Beginner Guide - 12 Tips Every New Player Must Know
In this First Berserker Khazan video, I'm going to be giving you guys ten tips to help you get off to the best possible start. These are things I wish I had known when I started playing this game. There are a lot of mechanics that kind of just get thrown at you. Some of these things you'll figure out eventually, and some of them you'll wish you'd known like 20 hours earlier. So that's what we're going to get into in this video.

Timestamp:
0:00 - The First Berserker Khazan Tips for New Players
0:17 - Use Extra Healing When Needed
0:55 - Vengeance Points & Extra Damage
1:29 - Hidden Chest in the Crevice
1:50 - Use Lanterns When You Need Them
3:05 - Don’t Ignore Status Effects
3:52 - Use Soulstones for Health Recovery
4:34 - You Can Teleport to Any Blade Nexus You Have Been
5:35 - Speak With NPCs After Each Mission
6:00 - You Can Exchange Crafting Materials at Blacksmith
6:26 - Sets & How to Use Them
8:04 - Make
title: First Berserker Khazan Beginner Guide - 12 Tips Every New Player Must Know
